channel.title: Open Source Projects
channel.description:
Hey, just out of curiosity how many people here have worked with any Open source projects. So far i only worked/ contributed to one Gwyddion: http://gwyddion.net/gwyddion.php [while i was working]
I was wondering if any of you are working on any open source projects, if so do tell, i am looking for something interesting to join in on. Also i been thinking of starting my own, (in C++), something along the lines of data encryption libraries.
